    "The stock market is a crucial conduit for businesses to raise funds from investors and is a financial ecosystem connecting corporations and investors (Zhong and Enke 2019).",
    "The enormous trading volume and profitability of the stock market continues to attract investors and traders keen to employ this system to maximize their profits (Adam et al. 2016).",
    "However, the stock market has the characteristic of extreme volatility and nonstationarity, making it prone to numerous complicated shocks and games.",
    "Consequently, there are obstacles to devising solid trading methods and making profitable investment decisions (Gu and Peng 2019).",
